  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Featured</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="gem-c-image-card gem-c-image-card--large ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="alt=""" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69142/s712_facialrecog.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-26">26 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/ethical-principles-to-guide-police-facial-recognition-trials">Ethical principles to guide police facial recognition trials</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The independent Biometrics and Forensics Ethics Group has published an interim report into facial recognition and identified ethical principles to consider.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Note taking." src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/62225/s465_note_taking.png"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
