        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/publications/ethical-principles-biometrics-and-forensics-ethics-group">Ethical principles: Biometrics and Forensics Ethics Group</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Set of ethical principles developed by the Biometrics and Forensics Ethics Group.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="alt=""" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/68904/s465_penpaper.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-12">12 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/ethics-group-to-oversee-use-of-large-data-sets-by-the-home-office">Ethics group to oversee use of large data sets by the Home Office</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The remit of the Biometrics and Forensics Ethics Group has been expanded to provide independent review of the use of large data sets by the department.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="A picture of files." src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/61298/s465_files_pic.png"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-03-19">19 March 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/new-members-appointed-to-biometrics-and-forensics-ethics-group">New members appointed to Biometrics and Forensics Ethics Group</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Seven experts take up positions on the ethics group.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
